&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is a place where you can bring your purpose to life through the work that you do, creating a safer world through our cyber security SaaS portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our culture of flexibility, trust, and continual learning means you will be recognized for your growth, and for the impact you make on our success. You will be surrounded by people who challenge, support, and inspire you to be the best version of yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;The Role&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust&amp;nbsp;is seeking a Software Development Engineer to contribute to the development and maintenance of core platform services that support multiple product lines. As part of the Platform Core Services team, you will collaborate with engineers, product managers, and stakeholders to build scalable, secure, and reliable services, including authentication &amp;amp; authorization (AuthN/AuthZ), onboarding, RBAC, reporting, auditing, notifications, and platform APIs. This is an exciting opportunity for an engineer looking to grow their&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;in platform engineering, infrastructure automation, and operational excellence while working in a high-impact, cross-functional environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and Maintain Core Services – Implement and enhance high-quality, scalable microservices that support platform-wide capabilities, ensuring modularity and extensibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on System Design &amp;amp; Implementation – Work with senior engineers and product managers to translate requirements into well-structured, maintainable, and testable software solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhance System Reliability &amp;amp; Observability – Contribute to logging, monitoring, and alerting solutions using Datadog to ensure visibility and proactive issue resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Infrastructure as Code &amp;amp; Cloud Automation – Assist in automating cloud infrastructure management using Terraform, Terragrunt, and CI/CD pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve Engineering Efficiency – Participate in code reviews, advocate for engineering best practices, and contribute to documentation to ensure team-wide knowledge sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Operational Excellence – Help troubleshoot and resolve production issues, participate in incident response, and propose solutions for long-term stability and scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Team Collaboration – Work with product managers, designers, and engineers from other teams to deliver features and platform enhancements that meet business and customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and Maintain Core Services – Implement and enhance high-quality, scalable microservices that support platform-wide capabilities, ensuring modularity and extensibility.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on System Design &amp;amp; Implementation – Work with senior engineers and product managers to translate requirements into well-structured, maintainable, and testable software solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhance System Reliability &amp;amp; Observability – Contribute to logging, monitoring, and alerting solutions using Datadog to ensure visibility and proactive issue resolution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Infrastructure as Code &amp;amp; Cloud Automation – Assist in automating cloud infrastructure management using Terraform,&amp;nbsp;Terragrunt, and CI/CD pipelines.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve Engineering Efficiency – Participate in code reviews, advocate for engineering best practices, and contribute to documentation to ensure team-wide knowledge sharing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Operational Excellence – Help troubleshoot and resolve production issues,&amp;nbsp;participate&amp;nbsp;in incident response, and propose solutions for long-term stability and scalability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Team Collaboration – Work with product managers, designers, and engineers from other teams to deliver features and platform enhancements that meet business and customer needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Nice To Have&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software Development Experience – experience in software development and delivering cloud-based or distributed systems with an emphasis on scalability and security.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency&amp;nbsp;in Modern Programming Languages – Experience with one or&amp;nbsp;more of&amp;nbsp;C#, Go, Java, Python, or similar languages.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of&amp;nbsp;Cloud &amp;amp; Infrastructure – Familiarity with AWS, Google Cloud, or Azure, including cloud-native development principles.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Infrastructure as Code &amp;amp; DevOps Practices – Basic knowledge of Terraform, CI/CD tools (e.g., GitHub Actions, Jenkins,&amp;nbsp;ArgoCD), and containerization technologies like Docker and Kubernetes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational Awareness – Understanding of monitoring, logging, and observability tools (e.g., Datadog, Prometheus) and how they support system health.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Problem-Solving Skills – Ability to debug, analyze issues, and propose well-structured solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaboration &amp;amp; Communication – Comfortable working with other engineers, product teams, and stakeholders in a cross-functional, agile environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Who You Are&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive problem solver who enjoys taking ownership of tasks and seeing them through completion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team player who values open collaboration and constructive feedback.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone who continuously learns and adapts, eager to expand their technical&amp;nbsp;expertise.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented and mindful of trade-offs between short-term solutions and long-term maintainability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about delivering quality software that is secure, scalable, and meets customer needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Better Together&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity. Inclusion. They’re more than just words for us. They are the guiding values of how we build our teams, cultivate leaders, and create a culture where people feel connected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take care of our employees so they can take care of our customers. Customers who&amp;nbsp;come from all walks of life just like us. We hire incredible people from diverse backgrounds because when we are different together, we are stronger together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;About Us&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is the worldwide leader in intelligent identity and access security, enabling organizations to protect identities, stop threats, and deliver dynamic access. We are leading the charge in innovating identity-first security and are trusted by 20,000 customers, including 75 of the Fortune 100, plus a global ecosystem of partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn more at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.beyondtrust.com/&quot;&gt;www.beyondtrust.com&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
